citation: Government Business Enterprises and State-owned Companies Legislation Amendment Act 2009 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Government Business Enterprises and State-owned Companies Legislation Amendment Act 2009 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Government Business Enterprises and State-owned Companies Legislation Amendment Act 2009 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
